 project design is currently being finalized.\n\nPage 3 of 7\nAgenda Item # 4.B.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4206, "end_char_idx": 4448, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "68210725-9d9c-4ae4-9873-4aa2c61847ea": {"__data__": {"id_": "68210725-9d9c-4ae4-9873-4aa2c61847ea", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "3eac956b-014d-49ca-b04f-5f7df70bd95c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c6feb49d827d0663fdd2a4c383bbc6c52c8b98f580773627f414f1113d004a75", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "19ab35e1-a537-477e-8368-faad02e683c7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c7e917ac2a9fc498972d4790d25aca69cbed3a7fa23c63d02f2be4220729dded", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be\n\nEstimated Schedule:\n\n\u0083 Complete Design: July, 2023 \u0083 Begin Construction: Fall 2023\n\nTrancas Canyon Park Playground\n\n\u00be Updates:\n\n\u0083 Staff  is  currently  working  on  the  final  design  plans.\n\n    Based  upon input from Community Services, the construction of this project must be started no earlier than November 2023.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4450, "end_char_idx": 4772, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "19ab35e1-a537-477e-8368-faad02e683c7": {"__data__": {"id_": "19ab35e1-a537-477e-8368-faad02e683c7", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "68210725-9d9c-4ae4-9873-4aa2c61847ea", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "a820687d75de6a9c8d8406298047fe9f2ae282d109581a53fc0e8d267de7b649", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "620c6b16-4a78-4b92-ae0e-e443c9f4b148", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3f4044f9f48e5f40c058481ec73bb29a839456bf8b7d19dc068a1a3782a470d8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be\n\nEstimated Schedule: \u0083 Complete Design: Winter 2023\n\n\u0083 Advertise: Winter 2023 \u0083 Begin Construction:\n\n Winter/Spring 2024\n\nMalibu Canyon Road Traffic Study\n\n\u00be Project Description:\n\n  This project will consist of performing a traffic study on Malibu Canyon Road near Harbor Vista Drive and Potter Lane to determine if any feasible traffic safety improvements can be constructed at this location.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 4774, "end_char_idx": 5169, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "620c6b16-4a78-4b92-ae0e-e443c9f4b148": {"__data__": {"id_": "620c6b16-4a78-4b92-ae0e-e443c9f4b148", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "19ab35e1-a537-477e-8368-faad02e683c7", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "c7e917ac2a9fc498972d4790d25aca69cbed3a7fa23c63d02f2be4220729dded", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "b691e648-8c55-4f9c-a350-836b461a72ec", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "18175a6acbc011ad2180d3c88bb0371a95b3626e5196aa10bed0ea1dcc4dc773", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be Project Updates:\n\n\u0083 City issued RFQ/P for design services and received proposals in May 2023.\n\n\u0083 Staff will be evaluating the proposal and recommending a contract to City Council in August 2023.\n\nKanan Dume Biofilter\n\n\u00be Project  Description:\n\n    This  project  was  identified  in  the  City\u2019s  Enhanced Watershed Management Plan (EWMP).", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5171, "end_char_idx": 5511, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "b691e648-8c55-4f9c-a350-836b461a72ec": {"__data__": {"id_": "b691e648-8c55-4f9c-a350-836b461a72ec", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "620c6b16-4a78-4b92-ae0e-e443c9f4b148", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "3f4044f9f48e5f40c058481ec73bb29a839456bf8b7d19dc068a1a3782a470d8", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "1819b494-a079-49ff-aaf9-49b68cbffdc6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ad2cbfcd384278222f30b61ce757835d7e47c0f790754877e506b934c8aea1aa", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "This project includes the installation of  a  biofilter  on  Kanan  Dume  Drive  to  capture  and  treat  stormwater.  The project  is  intended  to  assist  with  Municipal  Separate  Storm  Sewer  System (MS4) Discharge Permit requirements.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5512, "end_char_idx": 5754, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "1819b494-a079-49ff-aaf9-49b68cbffdc6": {"__data__": {"id_": "1819b494-a079-49ff-aaf9-49b68cbffdc6", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "b691e648-8c55-4f9c-a350-836b461a72ec", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "18175a6acbc011ad2180d3c88bb0371a95b3626e5196aa10bed0ea1dcc4dc773", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "bb5d43c5-d4cc-476a-81d1-8e350237354c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "68a80c509ef95581399a8b3182271f5328f5739530043af2bc3a416386c86466", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be Project Updates:\n\n\u0083 Complete Design: Spring 2024\n\n\u0083 Begin Construction: Spring/Summer 2024\n\nPCH Median Improvements at Paradise Cove and Zuma Beach\n\n\u00be Project Description:\n\n  This project was identified in the 2015 PCH Safety Study and includes installing new raised medians and improvements.  New raised medians are proposed east and west of PCH and Paradise Cove Road.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 5756, "end_char_idx": 6128, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "bb5d43c5-d4cc-476a-81d1-8e350237354c": {"__data__": {"id_": "bb5d43c5-d4cc-476a-81d1-8e350237354c", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "1819b494-a079-49ff-aaf9-49b68cbffdc6", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "ad2cbfcd384278222f30b61ce757835d7e47c0f790754877e506b934c8aea1aa", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "f2e16791-c225-43b7-ae88-04fc02aabdd2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e51e1539d18af9405decbdd72dbb6a78ae1162c44c912673bd6a92e48e518e7c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "The proposed improvements also include the relocation of the existing bus stop and new signage.\n\n  The project will also include the installation of new raised medians on PCH in the areas where the double yellow lines exist in the vicinity of Zuma Beach, specifically where the yellow paddles are installed.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 6130, "end_char_idx": 6437, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "f2e16791-c225-43b7-ae88-04fc02aabdd2": {"__data__": {"id_": "f2e16791-c225-43b7-ae88-04fc02aabdd2", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "bb5d43c5-d4cc-476a-81d1-8e350237354c", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "68a80c509ef95581399a8b3182271f5328f5739530043af2bc3a416386c86466", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "dc0a5378-c341-489a-b4ba-d0e2ae3cbb62", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "bb1ed19692eb5e2c4c44c11b7dc6dc81a90f422c54620a2dbb080bb872c67d2c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "\u00be Project  Updates:\n\n  City  received  funding  agreement  from  Measure  M  and  is scheduled for City Council on July 10, 2023 for execution.Page 4 of 7\nAgenda Item # 4.B.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 6439, "end_char_idx": 6612, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "dc0a5378-c341-489a-b4ba-d0e2ae3cbb62": {"__data__": {"id_": "dc0a5378-c341-489a-b4ba-d0e2ae3cbb62", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": [], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "d085eaec-33da-425d-882e-f4838b1193e6", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {}, "hash": "cb964ae1a2debb31f53a01df1ce7b0fe03c3e84a6fad888ec2ce82998e8d0b0c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "f2e16791-c225-43b7-ae88-04fc02aabdd2", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e51e1539d18af9405decbdd72dbb6a78ae1162c44c912673bd6a92e48e518e7c", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "fd64f7b3-899f-4457-a397-8f95c1f9df83", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "47abae6b6c19ce1b14e68fb60aced946bcba0390dab8a7c215238a00c0791f19", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "City Traffic Signals Backup Power\n\n\u00be Project  Description:\n\n    This  project  will  include  upgrading  the  backup  power system to the City\u2019s traffic signals on Civic Center Way, Webb Way, Malibu Canyon Road, and Winter Canyon Road\n\n\u00be Updates: Project is in the preliminary design phase\n\n\u00be Project Schedule: Design is anticipated to be completed July, 2023\n\nPage 5 of 7\nAgenda Item # 4.B.", "mimetype": "text/plain", "start_char_idx": 6614, "end_char_idx": 7005, "metadata_seperator": "\n", "text_template": "{metadata_str}\n\n{content}", "class_name": "TextNode"}, "__type__": "1"}, "fd64f7b3-899f-4457-a397-8f95c1f9df83": {"__data__": {"id_": "fd64f7b3-899f-4457-a397-8f95c1f9df83", "embedding": null, "metadata": {}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": [], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": 